.Dd $Mdocdate: June 26 2008 $
.Dt CLCS 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm clcs
.Nd Cirrus Logic CS4280/CS4610/CS4615 audio device
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "clcs*  at pci?"
.Cd "audio* at clcs?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the Cirrus Logic CS4280 chip, as well as
for CS461x.
.Sh FILES
The driver needs a firmware file,
which is loaded on demand when the device is attached:
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width Ds -offset indent -compact
.It Pa /etc/firmware/cs4280
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr ac97 4 ,
.Xr audio 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver appeared in
.Ox 2.8 .
